---
title: Tender Lamb Rump & Mushroom Gravy with Dauphinoise Potatoes & Garlicky Beans
description: Lamb rump is usually served drizzled in a mint sauce, but we dare you try out this mushroom gravy, decadent and rich in earthy tones. Trust us, when it comes to lamb, a mushroom gravy is the new mint sauce.
